invalid type: string "From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia\nIndian industrialist and philanthropist (1937–2024)\nThis article is about the former chairman of Tata Sons. For the philanthropist and grandfather of Tata, see Ratanji Tata. For the father of JRD Tata, see Ratanji Dadabhoy Tata.\nRatan Naval TataGBE\nva Jayate\u{a0}(Sanskrit)\"Truth Alone Triumphs\"[1]Anthem:\u{a0}Jana Gana Mana\u{a0}